{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013iMET3Wi87KNkkGZXg7wCA","type":"tool_result","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# Rollback script: reverts non-default CockroachDB configuration to factory defaults.\n# Configuration snapshot taken 2026-06-14 from namespace cockroachdb, pod crdb-cluster-0.\n#\n# NON-DEFAULT STATE FOUND:\n#   cluster setting  kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate  = 1.0 MiB  (default: 32 MiB)\n#   cluster setting  diagnostics.reporting.enabled   = true     (default: false)\n#   zone config      RANGE default  gc.ttlseconds    = 14400 s  (default: 90000 s / 25 h)\n#\n# EXCLUDED (intentionally not reverted):\n#   cluster.secret  — cluster identity UUID; resetting breaks replication\n#   version         — cluster upgrade level; CockroachDB does not support downgrade\n#\n# Do NOT run until a change window is open. All three changes take effect immediately\n# and alter live cluster behaviour (GC cadence, rebalance throughput, telemetry).\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nNAMESPACE=\"${NAMESPACE:-cockroachdb}\"\nPOD=\"${POD:-crdb-cluster-0}\"\nCOCKROACH=\"./cockroach\"\n\nsql() {\n  kubectl -n \"$NAMESPACE\" exec \"$POD\" -- \"$COCKROACH\" sql --insecure -e \"$1\"\n}\n\necho \"=== [1/3] Resetting kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate to default (32 MiB) ===\"\nsql \"RESET CLUSTER SETTING kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate;\"\n\necho \"=== [2/3] Resetting diagnostics.reporting.enabled to default (false) ===\"\nsql \"RESET CLUSTER SETTING diagnostics.reporting.enabled;\"\n\necho \"=== [3/3] Resetting RANGE default gc.ttlseconds to default (90000 s) ===\"\nsql \"ALTER RANGE default CONFIGURE ZONE USING gc.ttlseconds = 90000;\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Post-rollback verification: remaining non-default cluster settings ===\"\nsql \"SELECT variable, value, default_value\n     FROM crdb_internal.cluster_settings\n     WHERE value != default_value\n     ORDER BY variable;\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Post-rollback verification: RANGE default zone config ===\"\nsql \"SELECT target, raw_config_sql\n     FROM crdb_internal.zones\n     WHERE target = 'RANGE default';\"\n\necho \"Rollback complete.\"","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1c2c1e21-a247-40e9-a634-bebedab6ee90","uuid":"b28a99f9-7b71-4a37-a924-93d0f9181327","timestamp":"2026-06-14T06:05:47.231Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# Rollback script: reverts non-default CockroachDB configuration to factory defaults.\n# Configuration snapshot taken 2026-06-14 from namespace cockroachdb, pod crdb-cluster-0.\n#\n# NON-DEFAULT STATE FOUND:\n#   cluster setting  kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate  = 1.0 MiB  (default: 32 MiB)\n#   cluster setting  diagnostics.reporting.enabled   = true     (default: false)\n#   zone config      RANGE default  gc.ttlseconds    = 14400 s  (default: 90000 s / 25 h)\n#\n# EXCLUDED (intentionally not reverted):\n#   cluster.secret  — cluster identity UUID; resetting breaks replication\n#   version         — cluster upgrade level; CockroachDB does not support downgrade\n#\n# Do NOT run until a change window is open. All three changes take effect immediately\n# and alter live cluster behaviour (GC cadence, rebalance throughput, telemetry).\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nNAMESPACE=\"${NAMESPACE:-cockroachdb}\"\nPOD=\"${POD:-crdb-cluster-0}\"\nCOCKROACH=\"./cockroach\"\n\nsql() {\n  kubectl -n \"$NAMESPACE\" exec \"$POD\" -- \"$COCKROACH\" sql --insecure -e \"$1\"\n}\n\necho \"=== [1/3] Resetting kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate to default (32 MiB) ===\"\nsql \"RESET CLUSTER SETTING kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate;\"\n\necho \"=== [2/3] Resetting diagnostics.reporting.enabled to default (false) ===\"\nsql \"RESET CLUSTER SETTING diagnostics.reporting.enabled;\"\n\necho \"=== [3/3] Resetting RANGE default gc.ttlseconds to default (90000 s) ===\"\nsql \"ALTER RANGE default CONFIGURE ZONE USING gc.ttlseconds = 90000;\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Post-rollback verification: remaining non-default cluster settings ===\"\nsql \"SELECT variable, value, default_value\n     FROM crdb_internal.cluster_settings\n     WHERE value != default_value\n     ORDER BY variable;\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Post-rollback verification: RANGE default zone config ===\"\nsql \"SELECT target, raw_config_sql\n     FROM crdb_internal.zones\n     WHERE target = 'RANGE default';\"\n\necho \"Rollback complete.\"","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SyMhT7H5UL1gysK1nYpkgR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ConfigMap `rollback-rehearsal` is created and verified. The live cluster is unchanged.\n\n**What was found and what the script reverts:**\n\n| # | Type | Setting | Current (non-default) | Will revert to |\n|---|------|---------|-----------------------|----------------|\n| 1 | Cluster setting | `kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate` | 1.0 MiB | 32 MiB (default) |\n| 2 | Cluster setting | `diagnostics.reporting.enabled` | true | false (default) |\n| 3 | Zone config | `RANGE default` `gc.ttlseconds` | 14400 s (4 h) | 90000 s (25 h, default) |\n\n**Intentionally excluded from the script:**\n- `cluster.secret` — auto-generated cluster identity UUID; resetting it would break inter-node replication.\n- `version = 24.1` — the cluster's upgrade level; CockroachDB does not support version downgrade.\n\nAll other zone entries (`DATABASE system`, `RANGE meta`, `RANGE liveness`, etc.) match the system-internal defaults CockroachDB sets on every new cluster and were not touched.\n\nThe script uses `RESET CLUSTER SETTING` for the two cluster settings (idiomatic — removes the explicit override and lets the built-in default apply), and an explicit `CONFIGURE ZONE USING gc.ttlseconds = 90000` for the zone config. It also runs post-rollback verification queries so the operator can confirm the state after execution."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":730,"cache_read_input_tokens":40289,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":730},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1c2c1e21-a247-40e9-a634-bebedab6ee90","uuid":"6633b8fa-0ab7-45ea-9e04-60231ca13687","request_id":"req_011Cc2ecAhA5VCUkviqMN8